data.description: If a beautiful open concept, Chalet style home, in a great lake front community with your own boat slip is what you are looking for, you have found it. This house features 1674 sq ft of living space ,including 3 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, great kitchen with granite counter tops, living room with gas fire place and a nice 12x20 screened in porch along with a wrap around deck and beautiful hardscape and a brick grill pit. There is about 1,200 sq ft of finished walk out basement that is not in the square footage until you add your own mini spit system. The french doors lead out to the hot tub that will convey with the  property. Then there is a 2 car 28x28  garage with an unfinished loft for more potential living or great office space. So if you are looking for a house set up for entertaining, swimming in the lake, and boating this house is for you. Call for a showing today!
